Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:10.99,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:13.73,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,可以坐你旁邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:15.52,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,當然 請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:17.07,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:21.31,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,有你的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:22.53,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:25.27,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:31.25,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,請接收來電
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:36.88,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,你好 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:38.85,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,您是?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.34,0:00:42.30,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,我啊…我是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:44.76,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,請告訴我您的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:48.57,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,抱歉哦 我沒有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:50.74,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,找我有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:53.13,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,你幾歲了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:55.33,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,小學六年級
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:57.58,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,是嗎 獨自一人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:00:59.17,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:02.04,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,真了不起啊 是要去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:04.61,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,去祖父家裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:08.10,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,父母忙於工作 要晚一點才能來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:09.91,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,你在說謊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.28,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,為什麼覺得我在說謊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:14.68,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,不需要什麼理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:17.17,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,你都已經知道答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:20.87,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,您對我的情況究竟瞭解多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:23.73,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,幾乎什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:27.59,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,但我知道你對這個世界的構造
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:31.48,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,懷有某種難以名狀的不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:34.17,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:36.72,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,因為我是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:40.15,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,我認為現實中不存在魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:43.04,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,再說我也並沒懷有任何的不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:46.58,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼搭乘了這輛電車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:51.09,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,你正在尋找自己的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.11,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,我覺得並不存在那樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:57.02,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,存在的 就在這輛列車行駛的方向上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.82,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,能夠找到你的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:03.13,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,但一旦踏入那裡 你就再也回不到過去的生活中了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:05.58,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,因為那裡是你理應存在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.81,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,會揪住你 再也不放開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:11.39,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,看看窗外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:15.05,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,你不可以翻過那座山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:19.10,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,不可以踏進對面的那座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:22.44,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,你是指…咲良田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:23.50,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.65,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,咲良田會將你囚禁在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:29.09,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,淺井惠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:32.02,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,如果你愛著如今生存著的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.22,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,就在下一站下車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:37.75,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,為什麼知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:39.55,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,你說呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:42.32,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,…因為您是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:45.96,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,恭喜你 滿分的答案
